<p><strong>Large giant, lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 16 (chain mail)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 110 (13d10+39)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., fly 30 ft.</p>

